# Keep the deployment to what the web app needs: the engine package,
# the web app, the static frontend, and the demo weights.
# pyproject.toml is hidden so Vercel installs from requirements.txt with pip;
# otherwise uv sync would pull the train group's torch (~4.5 GB bundle).
.claude/
tests/
training/
pyproject.toml
uv.lock
# Root-anchored: the repo-root original is not deployed, but the copy the
# site serves (web/static/icon.png) must be.
/icon.png
/chess_lock.png
/chess_lock_1.png
README.md
*.bundle
__pycache__/
